title: Journal of Counseling Psychology

contents.note: Official journal site (full text also available for subscription or payment)

additional-note: A 1987 renewal for the 1959 book 'Counseling and Psychotherapy: Theory and Practice' by Cecil Helden Patterson mentions that part of the book was previously published in the Journal of Counsling Psychology.  We do not know the date of that prior publication, but a 1959 article might be covered by that renewal.  There are no other contribution renewals recorded for this serial.
